title: Building The Strongest Shaolin Temple In Another World
description: Building The Strongest Shaolin Temple In Another World ManhuaThe young Huo Yuanzhen crossed the alien world and became a minor faction—the Shaolin Abbot’s commandment. In order to save his life and complete the task of the “abbot system”, Huo Yuanzhen had to start to find ways to make Shaolin believers more and more prosperous. The rise of Shaolin made the surrounding factions panic. They secretly tried to suppress Shaolin, but they were beaten by Huo Yuanzhen.
